FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774476674
OL,3,CCold snap sweeps the UK, but could
OL,4,Cthat all be about to change?
OL,6,FDoes it stay slightly warmer from
OL,7,Ftomorrow?
OL,9,FYes and no. A little colder again on
OL,10,FFriday into Saturday, before milder
OL,11,Fair returns for Sunday - all very
OL,12,Fnormal fluctuations for late March but
OL,13,Fif you really want to know the 'feel'
OL,14,Fof how your day will be, ignore the
OL,15,Ftemperatures and look to the wind
OL,16,Fdirection - if it's a 'nippy
OL,17,Fnortherly', you're in for a chilly day!
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
